Put your specs all in one location\par
\par
Don\rquote t frustrate buyers by spreading the important facts all across your page. Create a spec sheet and be as detailed as possible. When we say detailed, we mean detailed. As in, don\rquote t stop at the make and model. There are many different iterations of a 2018 Honda Civic. Including the trim line in your copy gives the buyer a lot more useful information they can leverage to make an informed decision.\par
\par
What you should include in your spec sheet:\par
\par
    Overview\par
    Condition\par
    Make\par
    Model\par
    Year\par
    Trim\par
    Kilometres\par
    Body type\par
    Colour\par
    Seats\par
